System Requirements
- Node.js 18+
- npm 9+
- sqlite3
- Git

Backend packages:
express
prisma
@prisma/client
sqlite3
jsonwebtoken
express-jwt
multer
cors
uuid
bcrypt
dotenv

Frontend packages:
react
react-dom
vite
axios
@mui/material
@mui/icons-material
@emotion/react
@emotion/styled
qrcode.react
dayjs
@mui/x-date-pickers


How to run the project?

Install packages, run the following command for /frontend and /backend folder:
npm install


Set up Prisma:
npx prisma migrate dev

Seed database:
node prisma/seed.js

Run backend:
npm start

Run frontend:
npm run dev